{
  "stem": "20088.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we never had any heating in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then there were-- each block had about 500 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And each camp had on both sides 10 barracks of those.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So in each little camp, there were already thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And at the end of each of those 10 blocks, there was a toilet and washing facilities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were allowed to go twice a day to the toilet as a group, or wash once a day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And those bunk beds, they were just kind of cemented holds about a yard wide and a yard high, and three on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in each hole, 10 people were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So, I mean, we were all our Dutch, from our Dutch transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So with people we had made a little friends, we chose one of those bunk cubbyholes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then we got our sort of a liquid, and a ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they said, this is what you'll get every evening, just a piece of bread, and sort of a tea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That will be your food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And every evening and every morning, you have to stand appell, which was a role call of the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "All the camps had to be counted twice a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it takes about two hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you will stand behind your block, your barrack, again in rows of five so that it can be quickly counted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And as long as it takes-- if it rains, if it's freezing, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's what you do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So we got up at about 5:00 o'clock every morning, had to stand two hours appell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Then we had to go to our work commando, which varied.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And when we came back in the evening, again two hours appell.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
